channel.title: Moparscape not updated like the real rs
channel.description: Hi, I know this isnt really a hard question to answer, but i wanted to know why the moparscape client cant and isnt as updated as the real rs. A few days ago i logged into rs and saw all the new graphics etc. Is that because moparscape cant update anymore because fagex jagex are blocking it?!? Just wanna know thanks!
